org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint

类 TaskState

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.runtime.checkpoint.TaskState
  • 所有已实现的接口:
    Serializable

    public class TaskState
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Simple container class which contains the task state and key-value state handles for the sub tasks of a JobVertex. This class basically groups all tasks and key groups belonging to the same job vertex together.

      • getUnwrappedKvStates

        public Map<Integer,org.apache.flink.util.SerializedValue<StateHandle<?>>> getUnwrappedKvStates(Set<Integer> keyGroupPartition)
        Retrieve the set of key-value state key groups specified by the given key group partition set. The key groups are returned as a map where the key group index maps to the serialized state handle of the key group.
        参数:
        keyGroupPartition - Set of key group indices
        返回:
        Map of serialized key group state handles indexed by their key group index.
